there was a crocodile and his wife one when the crocodile was roaming around his house then he saw a monkey there and asked what do you want then the monkey
said that he want some fruit then the crocodile call her wife to give some fruit then her has given him some fruit and the monkey went away when he eat the fruits
then he find it sweert and he taught that if fruit is sweet and the crocodile's wife daily eat those fruit so her heart will also be sweety 
then he made aplan to kill corocodile and his wife and he went to crocodile home for dinner and he has knife in his pocket the lady crocodile saw him 
and she killed the monkey. 
 